Hi, Iâ€™m the NewsBreak Ad Assistant. How can I help?

When it comes to setting up your campaigns, selecting the right bidding strategy is crucial. Two common bidding strategies for Performance Advertisers are Maximize Conversions and Target CPA (Cost-Per-Acquisition). You can learn more about these strategies and when to use each one in this article: [How to choose a bidding strategy](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/21344263367053-How-to-choose-a-bidding-strategy).
